cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CC, cs.NE 

This paper deals with improving the performance of syntactic parsers, which is a common topic in computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of statistical PCFG parser suggests that this paper may also fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The modification of PTB representation may also involve some computational complexity (cs.CC) and optimization techniques (cs.NE).
